        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-07-01T14:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-07-01T14:00:00-05:00" n="94" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d94">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.24/6–2548: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Tientsin</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Smyth</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-07-01T15:00:00-04:00">July 1, 1948—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>145. View expressed Nanking’s tel. 118 to Tientsin repeated Dept at 1145, June 25
                    concurred in by Dept. (Sent Tientsin as 145, repeated Nanking as 966.)</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
